xt-align: center;">type</span>=3D<span style=3D"font-family: OpenSans, Rale=
way, Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; backgro=
und-color: #ffffff;">warning</span></strong>"</span></p>
</td>
<td style=3D"width: 32.2032%; height: 22.3843px;">Apenas em aplica=C3=A7=C3=
=B5es com o&nbsp;<strong>SweetAlert ativado.</strong></td>
