e">
			<tbody><tr><td class=3D"macros_tit">sc_call_api($profile, $arr_settings)=
<br></td></tr>
			<tr><td style=3D"border: none;">
				<table width=3D"800" class=3D"macros_desc_table">
					<tbody><tr>
						<td style=3D"border: none;">
							<p class=3D"body1">Esta macro possibilita a utiliza=C3=A7=C3=A3o das=
 APIs integradas ao Scriptcase nos eventos das aplica=C3=A7=C3=B5es.</p>
<p class=3D"body1">Ela pode ser utilizada com um <a href=3D"https://www.scr=
iptcase.com.br/docs/pt_br/v9/manual/07-ferramentas/12-api/01-visao-geral/" =
target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopener">Perfil de API</a> criado na interface ou=
 informando as credenciais da API no evento.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div id=3D"undefined" class=3D"block" style=3D"margin-bottom: 0px;"><h2 id=
=3D"">Detalhe dos Par=C3=A2metros</h2><table style=3D"border-collapse: coll=
apse; width: 97.8723%;" border=3D"1">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 10.0188%;"><strong class=3D"corpo1">Par=C3=A2metros</st=
rong></td>
<td style=3D"width: 52.7239%;"><strong class=3D"corpo1">Sintaxe</strong></t=
d>
<td style=3D"width: 37.2574%;"><strong class=3D"corpo1">Descri=C3=A7=C3=A3o=
</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 10.0188%; text-align: center;"><code><span style=3D"fon=
t-family: monospace;">profile</span></code></td>
<td style=3D"width: 52.7239%;">
<p><span style=3D"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: OpenSans, Raleway, Lato=
, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; background-color=
: #ffffff;">O nome do bot=C3=A3o do perfil pode ser informado utilizando&nb=
sp;<span style=3D"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">aspas duplas</=
span></span><span style=3D"font-family: OpenSans, Raleway, Lato, Arial, san=
s-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">=
,&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder; font=
-family: OpenSans, Raleway, Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-=
align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">aspas simples</span><span style=
=3D"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: OpenSans, Raleway, Lato, Arial, sans-=
serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">&n=
bsp;ou&nbsp;<strong>vari=C3=A1vel</strong>.</span><strong><br></strong></p>
<p><strong><span style=3D"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: OpenSans, Ralew=
ay, Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; backgrou=
nd-color: #ffffff;">Exemplo:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=3D"box-sizing=
: inherit; font-family: OpenSans, Raleway, Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-si=
ze: 16px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">Utiliza=C3=A7=C3=
=A3o da macro com um nome de perfil.</span></p>
<p><code><span style=3D"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: OpenSans, Raleway=
, Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; color: #7e=
8c8d;">sc_call_api(<strong><span style=3D"color: #000000;">'nome_do_perfil'=
</span></strong>);</span></code></p>
<p><strong><span style=3D"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: OpenSans, Ralew=
ay, Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; backgrou=
nd-color: #ffffff;">Exemplo:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=3D"box-sizing=
: inherit; font-family: OpenSans, Raleway, Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-si=
ze: 16px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">Utiliza=C3=A7=C3=
=A3o da macro com o valor vazio</span></p>
<p>// Neste caso o par=C3=A2metro <code>$array_settings</code> torna-se obr=
igat=C3=B3rio.<br><code><span style=3D"color: #7e8c8d;">sc_call_api(<span s=
tyle=3D"color: #000000;"><strong>""</strong></span>, $array_settings);</spa=
n></code></p>
</td>
<td style=3D"width: 37.2574%;">
<p><strong>Este par=C3=A2metro =C3=A9 obrigat=C3=B3rio.</strong></p>
<p>Ele recebe o <a href=3D"https://www.scriptcase.com.br/docs/pt_br/v9/manu=
al/07-ferramentas/12-api/01-visao-geral/" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopener=
">nome do perfil</a>&nbsp;configurado no menu "<strong>ferramentas &gt; API=
</strong>"</p>
<p>=C3=89 poss=C3=ADvel tamb=C3=A9m passar o valor vazio, neste caso, o par=
=C3=A2metro <code>$array_settings</code> torna-se obrigat=C3=B3rio.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 10.0188%; text-align: center;"><code><span style=3D"fon=
t-family: monospace;">settings</span></code></td>
<td style=3D"width: 52.7239%;">
<p>Este par=C3=A2metro recebe um array com as credenciais da API utilizada,=
 caso o par=C3=A2metro <code>profile</code> esteja vazio.</p>
<p><strong>Exemplo:</strong> Utiliza=C3=A7=C3=A3o da macro com o par=C3=A2m=
etro settings</p>
<p><code><span style=3D"color: #7e8c8d;"><span style=3D"color: #000000;">$<=
span style=3D"color: #7e8c8d;"><span style=3D"color: #000000;">arr_settings=
</span></span>&nbsp;=3D array( 'settings' =3D&gt; ['gateway' =3D&gt; 'mandr=
ill', 'api_key'=3D&gt; {api_key}] );</span></span></code><br><code><span st=
yle=3D"color: #7e8c8d;">sc_call_api("", <strong><span style=3D"color: #0000=
00;">$</span></strong><span style=3D"color: #000000;">arr_settings</span>);=
</span></code></p>
</td>
<td style=3D"width: 37.2574%;">
<p><strong>Este par=C3=A2metro =C3=A9 opcional</strong>, e deve ser utiliza=
do apenas se o par=C3=A2metro <code>profile</code> receber um valor vazio.<=
/p>
<p>Neste caso o par=C3=A2metro <strong><code>settings</code> </strong>torna=
-se obrigat=C3=B3rio j=C3=A1 que cont=C3=A9m os dados de acesso e credencia=
is da API utilizada.</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table><p>&nbsp;</p><hr></div>



