ss=3D"body1" id=3D"">Exemplos</h2><hr><p>Confira abaixo alguns exemplos de =
utiliza=C3=A7=C3=A3o da macro com o par=C3=A2metro <code>settings</code>.&n=
bsp;</p><p><strong>Exemplo 1 - Utiliza=C3=A7=C3=A3o b=C3=A1sica da macro co=
m o Mandrill</strong></p><pre>$settings =3D array( 'settings' =3D&gt; ['gat=
eway' =3D&gt; 'mandrill', 'api_key'=3D&gt; {api_key}]);
$mandrill =3D sc_call_api('', $settings);
</pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Exemplo 2 - Envio de e-mail utilizando o mand=
rill.</strong></p><pre>$txt_no_tags =3D strip_tags({msg});

$arr_merge =3D array(
                 'name'  =3D&gt; '',
                 'type'  =3D&gt; 'to',
                 'email' =3D&gt; 'exemplo@exemplo.com'
             );

$var_config =3D array( 'settings' =3D&gt; ['gateway' =3D&gt; 'mandrill', 'a=
pi_key'=3D&gt; {api_key}] );

$mandrill =3D sc_call_api('', $var_config);
$var_msg =3D array(
               'from_email'                     =3D&gt; {from_email},
               'from_name'                      =3D&gt; {from_name},
                'html'                          =3D&gt; {msg},
                'text'                          =3D&gt; $txt_no_tags,
                'to'                            =3D&gt; array($arr_merge), =
            =20
                'subject'                       =3D&gt; {subject},
                'important'                     =3D&gt; true,           =20
                'auto_text'                     =3D&gt; null,
                'auto_html'                     =3D&gt; null,
                'inline_css'                    =3D&gt; null,
                'metadata'                      =3D&gt; array('website' =3D=
&gt; 'www.scriptcase.net')
    );

$async =3D false;
$retorno =3D $mandrill-&gt;messages-&gt;send($var_msg, $async);
</pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Exemplo 3 - Enviando SMS utilizando clickatel=
l.</strong></p><pre>$var_config     =3D array(=20
  'message'     =3D&gt; [
    'to'      =3D&gt; {sms_to},
    'message'     =3D&gt; {sms_txt},
    ],
    'settings'    =3D&gt; [
    'gateway'   =3D&gt; {gateway},
    'auth_token'  =3D&gt; {auth_token},
    ]=20
);

sc_send_sms($var_config);
</pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Exemplo 4 - Usando a macro com PagSeguro</str=
ong></p><pre>  $arr_settings =3D [
            'gateway' =3D&gt; 'pagseguro',
