br', <span style=3D"color: #000000;"><strong>'_self'</strong></span>);</spa=
n></code></p>
<p><strong>Exemplo&nbsp;</strong><strong>abrindo </strong><strong>nova aba<=
/strong><br><span style=3D"color: #7e8c8d;"><code>sc_error_exit('app_Login'=
, <span style=3D"color: #000000;"><strong>'_blank'</strong></span>);</code>=
