, "Lado_Simb_Monetario")<br></td></tr>
			<tr><td style=3D"border: none;">
				<table width=3D"800" class=3D"macros_desc_table">
					<tbody><tr>
						<td style=3D"border: none;">
							<p class=3D"corpo1">Esta macro tem por objetivo a formata=C3=A7=C3=
=A3o de valores num=C3=A9ricos.</p>
<table style=3D"width: 741px;" border=3D"0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td align=3D"left" valign=3D"top" width=3D"15%"><strong class=3D"corpo1">Pa=
r=C3=A2metro<br></strong></td>
<td align=3D"left" valign=3D"top"><strong class=3D"corpo1">Descri=C3=A7=C3=
=A3o</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"corpo1" align=3D"left" valign=3D"top">Meu_Campo</td>
<td class=3D"corpo1" align=3D"left" valign=3D"top"><span class=3D"corpo1">V=
ari=C3=A1vel ou campo que contena o valor a ser formatado (O retorno ser=C3=
=A1 na pr=C3=B3pria vari=C3=A1vel).</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"corpo1" align=3D"left" valign=3D"top">Simb_Grp</td>
<td class=3D"corpo1" align=3D"left" valign=3D"top"><span class=3D"corpo1">S=
