		<a name=3D"sc_ldap_login" id=3D"sc_ldap_login"></a>
		<table cellpadding=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" class=3D"macros_desc_main_tabl=
e">
			<tbody><tr><td class=3D"macros_tit">sc_ldap_login($server, $version, $us=
er, $password, $dn, $group, $port, $biblioteca)<br></td></tr>
			<tr><td style=3D"border: none;">
				<table width=3D"800" class=3D"macros_desc_table">
					<tbody><tr>
						<td style=3D"border: none;">
							<p>A macro <code>sc_ldap_login</code> =C3=A9 respons=C3=A1vel por es=
tabelecer a conex=C3=A3o com o servidor LDAP (Lightweight Directory Access =
Protocol), permitindo conex=C3=A3o com&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"315" data=
-end=3D"340">Active Directory (AD)</strong>, e baliza o funcionamento das d=
emais macros do LDAP, atrav=C3=A9s do par=C3=A2metro $biblioteca que define=
 a biblioteca utilizada (LdapRecord ou adLdap).</p>
<h4>Sintaxe</h4>
<p><code>sc_ldap_login($server, $version =3D '', $user =3D '', $password =
=3D '', $dn =3D '', $group =3D '', $port, $biblioteca);</code></p>
<h4>Par=C3=A2metros</h4>
<table style=3D"border-collapse: collapse; width: 88.9709%;" border=3D"1">
<thead>
<tr style=3D"background-color: #ecf0f1;">
<td style=3D"width: 20.5043%; text-align: center;">Par=C3=A2metro</td>
<td style=3D"width: 79.4893%;">Descri=C3=A7=C3=A3o</td>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 20.5043%; text-align: center;"><code>$server</code></td=
>
<td style=3D"width: 79.4893%;">Endere=C3=A7o IP ou hostname do servidor LDA=
P.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 20.5043%; text-align: center;"><code>$version</code></t=
d>
<td style=3D"width: 79.4893%;">Vers=C3=A3o do protocolo LDAP a ser usada (e=
xemplo: <code data-start=3D"715" data-end=3D"718">3</code>). Se vazio, assu=
me a vers=C3=A3o padr=C3=A3o do servidor.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 20.5043%; text-align: center;"><code>$user</code></td>
<td style=3D"width: 79.4893%;">Nome de usu=C3=A1rio para autentica=C3=A7=C3=
=A3o no LDAP. Deve estar no formato esperado pelo servidor, como <code data=
-start=3D"879" data-end=3D"907">cn=3Dadmin,dc=3Dempresa,dc=3Dcom</code> ou =
<code data-start=3D"911" data-end=3D"929">user@empresa.com</code>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 20.5043%; text-align: center;"><code>$password</code></=
td>
<td style=3D"width: 79.4893%;">Senha do usu=C3=A1rio utilizado para login n=
o LDAP.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 20.5043%; text-align: center;"><code>$dn</code></td>
<td style=3D"width: 79.4893%;">Distinguished Name (DN) que define o ponto d=
e pesquisa dos usu=C3=A1rios. Exemplo: <code data-start=3D"1094" data-end=
=3D"1115">"dc=3Dempresa,dc=3Dcom"</code>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 20.5043%; text-align: center;"><code>$group</code></td>
<td style=3D"width: 79.4893%;">Opcionalmente, pode ser informado um grupo p=
ara verificar a associa=C3=A7=C3=A3o do usu=C3=A1rio.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 20.5043%; text-align: center;"><code>$port</code></td>
<td style=3D"width: 79.4893%;">Porta usada para conex=C3=A3o com o servidor=
 LDAP (<code data-start=3D"1283" data-end=3D"1288">389</code> para conex=C3=
=B5es normais e <code data-start=3D"1313" data-end=3D"1318">636</code> para=
 conex=C3=B5es seguras via SSL).</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 20.5043%; text-align: center;"><code>$biblioteca</code>=
</td>
<td style=3D"width: 79.4893%;">
<p data-start=3D"0" data-end=3D"100">Este par=C3=A2metro define qual biblio=
teca ser=C3=A1 utilizada para a conex=C3=A3o com o <strong data-start=3D"89=
" data-end=3D"97">LDAP</strong>.</p>
<ul data-start=3D"102" data-end=3D"357">
<li data-start=3D"102" data-end=3D"249"><strong data-start=3D"104" data-end=
=3D"136">Se o valor <code data-start=3D"117" data-end=3D"120">2</code> for =
informado</strong>, a macro utilizar=C3=A1 a <strong data-start=3D"158" dat=
a-end=3D"177">nova biblioteca</strong> (<code data-start=3D"179" data-end=
=3D"191">LdapRecord</code>), dispon=C3=ADvel a partir da vers=C3=A3o <stron=
g data-start=3D"224" data-end=3D"232">9.12</strong> do Scriptcase.</li>
<li data-start=3D"250" data-end=3D"357"><strong data-start=3D"252" data-end=
=3D"288">Se o par=C3=A2metro n=C3=A3o for informado</strong>, a macro conti=
nuar=C3=A1 utilizando a <strong data-start=3D"322" data-end=3D"343">bibliot=
eca antiga</strong> (<code data-start=3D"345" data-end=3D"353">adLdap</code=
>).</li>
</ul>
<p data-start=3D"359" data-end=3D"553" data-is-last-node=3D"">Esse controle=
 permite que projetos antigos continuem funcionando sem modifica=C3=A7=C3=
=B5es, enquanto novas implementa=C3=A7=C3=B5es podem se beneficiar da compa=
tibilidade e seguran=C3=A7a aprimoradas do <strong data-start=3D"538" data-=
end=3D"552">LdapRecord</strong>.</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4><strong>Exemplo de uso</strong></h4><pre><span class=3D"hljs-variable">=
$server</span> =3D <span class=3D"hljs-string">"ldap.meuservidor.com"</span=
>;
<span class=3D"hljs-variable">$version</span> =3D <span class=3D"hljs-strin=
g">"3"</span>;
<span class=3D"hljs-variable">$user</span> =3D <span class=3D"hljs-string">=
"cn=3Dadmin,dc=3Dempresa,dc=3Dcom"</span>;
<span class=3D"hljs-variable">$password</span> =3D <span class=3D"hljs-stri=
ng">"senha123"</span>;
<span class=3D"hljs-variable">$dn</span> =3D <span class=3D"hljs-string">"d=
c=3Dempresa,dc=3Dcom"</span>;
<span class=3D"hljs-variable">$group</span> =3D <span class=3D"hljs-string"=
>""</span>;
<span class=3D"hljs-variable">$port</span> =3D <span class=3D"hljs-number">=
