e">
			<tbody><tr><td class=3D"macros_tit">sc_send_mail_api($arr_settings)<br><=
/td></tr>
			<tr><td style=3D"border: none;">
				<table width=3D"800" class=3D"macros_desc_table">
					<tbody><tr>
						<td style=3D"border: none;">
							<p class=3D"corpo1">Esta macro permite o envio din=C3=A2mico de e-ma=
ils integrados com as APIs do <strong>Mandrill</strong> e <strong>Amazon SE=
S</strong>. =C3=89 poss=C3=ADvel tam=C3=A9m o envio de e-mail utilizando o =
protocolo <strong>SMTP</strong></p>
<blockquote style=3D"color: #4d4d4d;">Esta macro utliza os mesmos par=C3=A2=
metros do mandrill para envio de e-mail, independente do Gateway(Mandril, A=
mazon SES ou SMTP) selecionado. <a href=3D"https://mandrillapp.com/api/docs=
/messages.JSON.html#method=3Dsend" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopener">cliqu=
e aqui</a> e veja a lista dos par=C3=A2metros que pode ser utilizados.</blo=
ckquote>
<p>Esta macro contem um =C3=BAnico par=C3=A2metro "<strong>$arr_settings</s=
trong>", que recebe um array com as informa=C3=A7=C3=B5es de envio de e-mai=
l.</p>
<blockquote style=3D"color: #4d4d4d;">Para mais informa=C3=A7=C3=B5es sobre=
 os par=C3=A2metros o mandirll <a href=3D"https://mandrillapp.com/api/docs/=
messages.JSON.html" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopener">clique aqui</a></blo=
ckquote>
<table border=3D"0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td align=3D"left" width=3D"17%"><strong class=3D"corpo1">Par=C3=A2metro <b=
r></strong></td>
<td align=3D"left"><strong class=3D"corpo1">Descri=C3=A7=C3=A3o</strong></t=
d>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"corpo1" align=3D"left">$arr_settings</td>
<td class=3D"corpo1" align=3D"left">Array com as informa=C3=A7=C3=B5es para=
 a utiliza=C3=A7=C3=A3o das APIs.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>=C3=8Dndices do Array</strong></p>
<table border=3D"0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td align=3D"left" width=3D"17%"><strong class=3D"corpo1">=C3=8Dndices do A=
rray<br></strong></td>
<td align=3D"left"><strong class=3D"corpo1">Descri=C3=A7=C3=A3o</strong></t=
d>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"corpo1" align=3D"left">profile</td>
<td class=3D"corpo1" align=3D"left">Nome de alguma API j=C3=A1 configurada =
em "Ferramentas &gt; API", como pode ser visto no Exemplo 1. Ao informar um=
 profile, o =C3=ADndice <strong>settings</strong> n=C3=A3o deve ser informa=
do.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"corpo1" align=3D"left">settings</td>
<td class=3D"corpo1" align=3D"left">Configura=C3=A7=C3=B5es do servidor de =
envio de e-mail. As informa=C3=A7=C3=B5es devem est=C3=A1 de acordo com a A=
PI utilizada. Obs.: Ao informar as configura=C3=A7=C3=B5es o indice Profile=
 =C3=A9 desconsiderado.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"corpo1" align=3D"left">message</td>
<td class=3D"corpo1" align=3D"left">Mensagem que ser=C3=A1 enviada por e-ma=
il. Assunto, corpo, destinat=C3=A1rio, etc.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Exemplo 1:</strong> <strong>Envio de e-mail utilizando um Profil=
e pr=C3=A9 configurado em "Ferramentas &gt; API".</strong></p><pre><code>if=
({api_type} =3D=3D 'smtp' ){
	$var_config =3D array(
		'profile' =3D&gt; 'yahoo_example',

		'message' =3D&gt; [
			'html'          =3D&gt; {msg},
			'text'          =3D&gt; '',
			'to'            =3D&gt; $arr_merge,
			//'attachments' =3D&gt; array('/var/www/arquivo.txt','/var/www/arquivo2.=
txt'),
			'subject'       =3D&gt; {subject}
		]
	);
}

sc_send_mail_api($var_config);
</code></pre>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Exemplo 2:</strong> <strong>Envio de e-mail por SMTP</strong></p=
><pre><code>$smtp_server =3D "smtp.mail.yahoo.com";
$smtp_port =3D "465";
$smtp_user =3D "scriptcase.export";
$smtp_password =3D "scriptcase.export";
$from_email =3D "scriptcase.export@yahoo.com";
$from_name =3D "Scriptcase Export";

if ( {api_type} =3D=3D 'smtp' ){
	$var_config =3D array(

		'profile' =3D&gt; '',

		'settings' =3D&gt; [
				'gateway'       =3D&gt; 'smtp',
				'smtp_server'   =3D&gt; $smtp_server,
				'smtp_port'     =3D&gt; $smtp_port,
				'smtp_user'     =3D&gt; $smtp_user,
				'smtp_password' =3D&gt; $smtp_password,
				'from_email'    =3D&gt; $from_email,
				'from_name'     =3D&gt; $from_name
		],

		'message' =3D&gt; [
				   'html'          =3D&gt; {msg},
				   'text'          =3D&gt; '',
				   'to'            =3D&gt; $arr_merge,
				   //'attachments' =3D&gt; array('/var/www/arquivo.txt','/var/www/arqui=
vo2.txt'),
				   'subject'       =3D&gt; {subject}
		]
	);
}

sc_send_mail_api($var_config);
</code></pre>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Exemplo 3:</strong> <strong>Envio de e-mail usando o Mandrill</s=
trong></p><pre><code>if({api_type} =3D=3D 'mandrill' ){
	$var_config =3D array(
		'settings' =3D&gt; [
				   'gateway'       =3D&gt; 'mandrill',
				   'api_key'   	   =3D&gt; {api_key},
				   'from_email'    =3D&gt; {from_email},
				   'from_name'     =3D&gt; {from_name}
		],

		'message' =3D&gt; [
				   'html'          =3D&gt; {msg},
				   'text'          =3D&gt; '',
				   'to'            =3D&gt; array($arr_merge),
				   //'attachments' =3D&gt; array('/var/www/arquivo.txt','/var/www/arqui=
vo2.txt'),
				   'subject'       =3D&gt; {subject}
		]
	);
}

sc_send_mail_api($var_config);
</code></pre>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Exemplo 4:</strong> <strong>Envio de e-mail usando o Amazon SES<=
/strong></p><pre><code>if({api_type} =3D=3D 'ses' ){
	$var_config =3D array(
		'settings' =3D&gt;  [
	        'gateway' =3D&gt; 'ses',
	        'region' =3D&gt; {ses_region},
	        'api_key' =3D&gt; {api_key},
	        'api_secret' =3D&gt; {ses_secret},
	        'from_email'    =3D&gt; {from_email}
	    ],
	    'message' =3D&gt; [
	        'html'          =3D&gt; {msg},
	        'text'          =3D&gt; '',
	        'to'            =3D&gt; array($arr_merge),
	        'subject'       =3D&gt; {subject}
	    ]
	);
}

sc_send_mail_api($var_config);
</code></pre>
