						<td style=3D"border: none;">
							<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Esta macro calcula e retorna um=
 array com os valores estat=C3=ADsticos informados a partir de um array de =
valores num=C3=A9ricos.</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">S=C3=A3o necess=C3=A1rio dois par=C3=
=A2metros para a utiliza=C3=A7=C3=A3o da macro.<br></span></p>
<table style=3D"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;" border=3D"1">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th style=3D"width: 7.94698%; background-color: #dddddd; text-align: center=
; vertical-align: middle;"><strong>Par=C3=A2metro</strong></th>
<th style=3D"width: 33.1272%; background-color: #dddddd; text-align: center=
; vertical-align: middle;">Valor</th>
<th style=3D"width: 26.1224%; background-color: #dddddd; text-align: center=
; vertical-align: middle;"><strong>Descri=C3=A7=C3=A3o</strong></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 7.94698%; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">=
<span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">arr_val</span></td>
<td style=3D"width: 33.1272%; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;">
<p>Este par=C3=A2metro aceita apenas vari=C3=A1veis</p>
<p><strong>Exemplo de utiliza=C3=A7=C3=A3o</strong><br><code>$arr_val =3D a=
rray(5230.01,8374,625.45,8926.34,7000,523.78);</code><br><code><span style=
=3D"font-weight: 400;">sc_statistic($arr_val, <strong>$type</strong>);</spa=
n></code></p>
</td>
<td style=3D"width: 26.1224%; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;">
<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Vari=C3=A1vel contendo um array com os=
 valores num=C3=A9ricos de entrada.</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;"><strong>Par=C3=A2metros s=C3=A3o obrig=
at=C3=B3rio.</strong></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 7.94698%; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">=
<span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">tp_var</span></td>
<td style=3D"width: 33.1272%; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;">
<p>Este par=C3=A2metro aceita o valor ou uma vari=C3=A1vel.</p>
<p><strong>Exemplo informando o valor:</strong><br><span style=3D"font-weig=
ht: 400;"><code>sc_statistic($arr_val, <strong>'P'</strong>);</code></span>=
</p>
<p><strong>Exemplo utilizando uma vari=C3=A1vel</strong><br><code>$type =3D=
 'P';</code><br><code><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">sc_statistic($arr_v=
al, <strong>$type</strong>);</span></code></p>
<p>Lista das valores aceito no par=C3=A2metro.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>P</strong></li>
<li><strong>A</strong></li>
</ul>
</td>
<td style=3D"width: 26.1224%; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;">
<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Este par=C3=A2metro define o tipo de c=
=C3=A1lculo da <strong>vari=C3=A2ncia</strong>(=C3=ADndice 2) e do <strong>=
desvio padr=C3=A3o</strong>(=C3=ADndice 3) do array. <br><br>Os valores ace=
itos s=C3=A3o <strong>P</strong> e <strong>A</strong><br></span></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>P</strong> =3D&nbsp;populacional</li>
<li><strong>A</strong> =3DAmostral</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Par=C3=A2metros s=C3=A3o obrigat=C3=B3rio.</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</td>
